quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,16,"These are they who have purchased error for guidance, so their commerce was profitless. And they were not guided."
  2,17,"Their likeness is as the likeness of one who kindled a fire; then, when it lighted all around him, Allâh took away their light and left them in darkness. (So) they could not see."
  2,18,"They are deaf, dumb, and blind, so they return not (to the Right Path)."